OL,3,CGovernment rejects key Brook House
OL,4,Cmistreatment inquiry recommendation
OL,6,FThe Government has rejected an
OL,7,Finquiry's key recommendation made to
OL,8,Fprevent a repeat of the inhumane
OL,9,Ftreatment experienced by migrants in
OL,10,Fthe Brook House immigration centre
OL,11,Fscandal.
OL,13,FChairwoman Kate Eves said she was
OL,14,F"concerned" her inquiry's
OL,15,Frecommendations had not been accepted
OL,16,Fin full after the Home Office
OL,17,Fpublished its formal response to her
OL,18,Ffindings.
