OL,3,CGovernment rejects key Brook House
OL,4,Cmistreatment inquiry recommendation
OL,6,FMs Eves concluded there had been 19
OL,7,Fincidents of mistreatment against
OL,8,Fdetainees at the detention centre near
OL,9,FGatwick Airport in West Sussex over a
OL,10,Ffive-month period in 2017.
OL,12,FMaking a raft of recommendations for
OL,13,Fimprovement in September ` including
OL,14,Fintroducing a 28-day detention time
OL,15,Flimit ` she warned more people held in
OL,16,Fimmigration removal centres could face
OL,17,Finhumane treatment if the measures
OL,18,Fwere ignored, while reiterating how
OL,19,Fpast calls for Government reform had
OL,20,Ffallen on deaf ears.
