OL,3,CGovernment rejects key Brook House
OL,4,Cmistreatment inquiry recommendation
OL,6,FAt the time of the inquiry's final
OL,7,Freport, then home secretary Suella
OL,8,FBraverman acknowledged the "failings
OL,9,Fin both oversight and governance to
OL,10,Fprotect the welfare of detained
OL,11,Findividuals" at the centre and
OL,12,Fpromised her department would
OL,13,F"carefully consider the findings".
OL,15,FBut in its response, published on
OL,16,FTuesday, the Home Office said: "The
OL,17,FGovernment does not accept the
OL,18,Frecommendation that it should set a
OL,19,Ftime limit on detention.
