OL,6,F"A time limit would significantly
OL,7,Fimpair the ability to remove those who
OL,8,Fhave breached immigration laws and
OL,9,Frefused to leave the UK voluntarily.
OL,11,F"The Illegal Migration Act makes it
OL,12,Fclear that immigration detention must
OL,13,Fonly be used for a period of time that
OL,14,Fis reasonably necessary, in the
OL,15,Fopinion of the Secretary of State, for
OL,16,Fthe relevant immigration function to
OL,17,Fbe carried out."
