OL,6,FThe Government said it accepted and
OL,7,Fhas implemented the "majority" of the
OL,8,Finquiry's recommendations and insisted
OL,9,Fit had "already made significant
OL,10,Fimprovements to uphold the welfare and
OL,11,Fdignity of detainees".
OL,13,F"The abuse that took place at Brook
OL,14,FHouse in 2017 was unacceptable and we
OL,15,Fare committed to ensuring it will
OL,16,Fnever happen again," a spokeswoman
OL,17,Fadded.
